---
// Non-negotiable, directly under every hero. Fixes a live Google AI
// misattribution: Nadia founded and hosts, Monica teaches.
---

<div class="attribution">
  <p>Founded &amp; hosted by Nadia · Yoga led by senior teacher Monica of YogaMorphic</p>
</div>

<style>
  .attribution {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--cream-deep);
  }

  /* Quiet on purpose, per Nadia: the line exists for search engines and
     must stay on every page, but the visitor should barely register it.
     Small, sentence case, muted. */
  .attribution p {
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: none;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 8px 24px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.6px;
    color: var(--sage-dark);
  }
</style>
